Installation
------------

– First you need PHP 5.1 and a MySQL Database to use Facturier
– Create a MySQL database
– Install MySQL tables (facturier.sql)
– Modify include/config.php according to your system

Configuration
-------------

— Load index.php in a browser
— Click on Utilisateur and enter your informations
– If you want, secure the system by setting NEED_LOGIN constant to true
— Click on Clients and add a first Client

Now you are ready to create invoices.